  beta_y | y1 ON s;
  delta_y | y20 ON s;
  beta_s | s ON y20&1;
  ar_s | s ON s&1;
  s (resvar_s);

  %BETWEEN%
  mu BY y1-y20@1;
  mu;
  [mu];
  [y1-y20@0];

  [beta_y](a);
  [beta_s](b);

  mu day_ar night_ar-ar_s s WITH
     mu day_ar night_ar-ar_s s;

  MODEL CONSTRAINT:
  NEW(indirect);
  indirect = a * b;

  OUTPUT:

  PLOT:

  FACTOR = ALL (500);
